{"tid":398972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩係太古城3樓女廁漏左部手機既入黎","createTime":"2017-09-13T14:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T12:31:20.000Z","uid":20116,"like":606,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b418b7dac2dc28e4fae6b7b9b57ef6b0df9b1a","tid":398972,"uid":20116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩放工好急尿就即刻衝左去廁所 9點半左右啦<br />\n一推開廁格到門就見到有部電話放左係擺紙巾果個位上面 係部SamSung機<br />\n<br />\n我已經即刻開返門問哂洗緊手既人部電話係咪佢地既 但係無一個人係<br />\n所以我拎左去比個商場管理員 佢地會keep係控制室<br />\n<br />\n希望你睇到呢個post啦 返到去廁格搵唔返部電話唔洗驚 去搵商場管理員拎返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次小心啲啦去完廁所記得要拎返啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（其實我自己都試過係同一格漏電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/224433_a8e8e6cdbf15714657e1b4ed3c1051a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F224433_a8e8e6cdbf15714657e1b4ed3c1051a4.jpg&h=b6836461&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53393551f5199b4cb3cd9ba5167863773a4bd32a","tid":398972,"uid":20116,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be99c8f793adea58ab8f0adec55c242efaa74a0","tid":398972,"uid":20116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efed27336e70c294e6e194e36e84cb76794837f","tid":398972,"uid":20116,"like":0,"dis